block page
  .section.black-bg.p-b-0
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-6
          .m-b-lg
            h1.white Getting Started
            h4.white.opacity-70.m-y Spin up a node on the bitcoin network.
          p.white Bitcore is kind of like express but for bitcoin servers. Each bitcoin node will be full capable of monitoring the network, making transactions, and storing the blockchain..
        .col-lg-6
          img.width-100(src="/images/icosahedron-spheres.png")
  
  .section.white-bg
    .container
      .row.steps
        .col-lg-6
          h4 Install Bitcore
          p First install bitcore and then do some stuff
        .col-lg-6
          pre npm install -g bitcore

      .row.steps
        .col-lg-6
          h4 Create a node
          p We are going to create a bitcore node here and call it mynode
        .col-lg-6
          pre bitcore create mynode <br />cd mynode
          
      .row.steps
        .col-lg-6
          h4 Add a service
          p Install both the insight UI and the insight API full featured block exploreres.
        .col-lg-6
          pre bitcore add insight-api insight-ui

      .row.steps
        .col-lg-6
          h4 Start your node
          p First install bitcore and the do some stuff.
        .col-lg-6
          pre bitcore start



